Question: Is the controller in the top part or in the bottom of the image?

Reference Answer: bottom

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n233607.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=GET(image=IMAGE)
IMAGE0=CROP_ABOVE(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='controller')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'top' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'bottom'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
